# Getting Started with Gauge

This is an example markdown specification file.
Every heading in this file is a scenario.
Every bulleted point is a step.

To execute this specification, use
	npm test

## Simple mathematical expression
* Write in field "5+5*3"
* Click a button "Evaluate Expression"
* Assert result "20"
* Close results toast

## Simple series sum calculator
* Write in first field "1"
* Write in second field "2"
* Write in third field "4"
* Click a button "Evaluate Summation"
* Assert result "15"

